Name: Verify Create Account button is disabled for mismatched passwords
Description: Validates that the Create Account button remains disabled when password and confirm password do not match.

Name: Register: Fail when email already exists
Description: Registration with an already registered email should return 409 Conflict

Name: Verify GitHub Sign-In Redirect
Description: Ensures that clicking the 'Continue with GitHub' button redirects to GitHubâ€™s login page. Marks as expected behavior if integration is not completed yet.

Name: Verify user submits signup form with valid details
Description: Ensures that a user can fill and submit the signup form with valid credentials.

Name: Verify pricing options are visible after scrolling down the homepage
Description: Ensures that the 'SkillDev Pricing Models' section becomes visible when the user scrolls down on the homepage.

Name: Verify navigation from Forgot Password page back to Login page
Description: Ensures that clicking the 'Back to Login' button on the Forgot Password page correctly navigates the user to the Login page.

Name: Verify 'Start Practicing' navigates to Signup Page
Description: Ensures that clicking the 'Start Practicing' button on the homepage redirects the user to the signup page.

Name: Verify Create Account button is disabled for wrong password length
Description: Validates that the Create Account button remains disabled when password length not meet the required format.

Name: Verify navigation to Forgot Password page when clicked
Description: Ensures that clicking on the 'Forgot Password?' link from the Login page navigates the user to the Forgot Password page.

Name: Verify Groups menu navigates to Groups page
Description: Clicking the Groups menu should navigate to the Groups page.

Name: Verify 'Send Link' button activates after entering a valid email
Description: Ensures that the 'Send Link' button becomes enabled once a valid email is entered on the Forgot Password page.

Name: Verify Create Account button is disabled for wrong email format
Description: Validates that the Create Account button remains disabled when email does not meet the required format.

Name: Verify Leaderboard menu navigates to Leaderboard page
Description: Clicking the Leaderboard menu should navigate to the Leaderboard page.

Name: Verify Skill Arena menu navigates to Skill Arena page
Description: Clicking the Skill Arena menu should navigate to the Skill Arena page.

Name: Verify that user can navigate to Login Page from Homepage
Description: Ensures clicking the Login button on the homepage redirects to the Login Page where main elements are visible.

Name: Verify valid user can login and see Dashboard
Description: Ensures that entering valid credentials logs the user in and displays the Dashboard page with main elements visible.

Name: Verify Create Account button is disabled for empty signup form
Description: Validates that the Create Account button remains disabled when all signup fields are empty.

Name: Verify user navigates from the homepage to signup page
Description: This test ensures that user can navigate from the homepage to the signup page successfully.

Name: Verify that a valid user can log in and log out successfully
Description: Logs in using valid credentials, verifies dashboard is displayed, then logs out and verifies redirection to Login page.

Name: Verify login button is active
Description: Ensures the login button is active after entering valid credentials from test data file.

Name: Verify clicking Profile icon navigates to Settings page
Description: Clicking on profile icon should navigate user to the settings page.

Name: Verify Forgot Password page elements
Description: Ensures all key elements on the Forgot Password page are visible and interactable.

Name: Verify homepage elements are visible on load
Description: Ensures key homepage elements such as logo, Start Practicing and Learn More buttons are visible when the page loads.

Name: Verify Settings menu navigates to Settings page
Description: Clicking the Settings menu should navigate to the Settings page.

Name: Register: Success for valid user
Description: Valid registration should return success=true and correct user email

Name: Register: Fail for too short password
Description: Registration with too short password should return validation error

Name: Verify 'Send Link' button remains disabled when invalid email is entered
Description: Ensures that the 'Send Link' button stays inactive when an invalid email is entered on the Forgot Password page.

Name: Verify navigation to Signup page from Login page
Description: Ensures that clicking on the 'Sign up' link from the Login page redirects the user to the Signup page.

Name: Verify login button remains disabled when no credentials are entered
Description: Ensures that the login button cannot be clicked when both email and password fields are empty.

Name: Verify Sign in with Google button behavior
Description: Ensures that the 'Sign in with Google' button is visible, clickable, and handles integration failure gracefully.

Name: Verify error messages appear for invalid credentials
Description: Ensures both email and password validation messages appear when invalid credentials are entered and user clicks outside the input fields.

Name: Register: Fail for invalid users
Description: Registration with invalid inputs should return errors or conflict

Name: Verify Task menu navigates to Task page
Description: Clicking the Task menu should navigate to the Tasks page.

Name: Verify all main elements are visible on the Dashboard
Description: Ensures that logo, welcome text, profile icon, progress bar, and progress graph are visible after login.
